OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland damp with some haar in
OL,6,Fthe morning then brightening up in the
OL,7,Fafternoon with sunny intervals. Orkney
OL,8,Fdry for much of day, but mostly
OL,9,Fcloudy, then some patchy rain and haar
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,13,Fand night with some haar at times
OL,14,Falong with a few patches of rain.
OL,15,FBecoming breezier later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FDull start for Shetland with
OL,18,Fsome haar, but brightening up, then
OL,19,Frather cloudy but with a few sunny
OL,20,Fintervals along with the odd shower.
OL,21,FWinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
