OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,6,Fintervals and a few showers on Friday.
OL,7,FSaturday looks dry and bright with
OL,8,Fsome sunshine before rain and wind in
OL,9,Fthe evening. Sunday back to sunshine
OL,10,Fand scattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
